snippet.title: Warframe | Tokyo Game Show 2024 Mobile Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover Warframe and embark on a fast-paced, action-filled journey across the Origin System! Customize your loadout with over 50+ Warframes, along with hundreds of weapons and cosmetics built to suit your playstyle and your choice of fashion.

Start playing for free on mobile today with iOS! Learn more: https://wrfr.me/4geKQlG

Sign Up for Warframe: https://wrfr.me/3ZfiyS7

Join 70M+ registered players in Warframe, a cooperative, free-to-play third-person looter shooter set in a constantly evolving sci-fi universe. For more info, visit https://warframe.com.
